Package: ESMvis
Title: Visualising Experience Sampling Method Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Stulp", "Gert", email = "g.stulp@rug.nl", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Bringmann", "Laura", email = "l.f.bringmann@rug.nl ", 
           role = c("aut")))
Description: This package provides several ways to visualise experience
    sampling method data. Given data consisting of repeated measurement, 
    timelines, networks, and barcharts can be plotted to get a better insight
    into the changes over time. It relies heavily on ggplot2.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.2)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    tidyr,
    lubridate
